{"tid":268210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"支聯會全名係乜都唔記得  李卓人：六四與愛國與否不重要","createTime":"2017-06-03T00:40:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T06:48:19.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"43af8b9511eeb406b621b4ffbf59d59aa9b2840b","tid":268210,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T00:40:50.000Z","msg":"支聯會全名係乜？<br />\n怕且李卓人年年食數百萬港元既六四人血饅頭, 食左28年已經食滯左唔記得啦<br />\n<br />\n支聯會全名 = 香港市民支援<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">愛國</span></span>民主運動聯合會<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170603/56776174\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170603%2F56776174&d=oDXEYGnpFcyUeXg9UHvZKBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=d8c322b6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20170603%2F56776174&h=ee531a9c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20170603/56776174</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">李卓人認為愛國與否不重要</span></span>，令他萬料不到反而是年輕人認為「六四唔關我事」，「20年前董建華叫我哋放下包袱，估唔到今時今日年輕人叫我哋放下包袱」。他指中港根本難以切割，「張德江搞我哋、人大8.31搞我哋，你話中國唔關我哋事？你唔結束專政，專政就嚟搞我哋」。他認為要對抗暴政，就要刺中六四這個死穴。"},{"pid":"cc668ca321f5321f4aa6dec516948a2d22830c84","tid":268210,"uid":21716,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T00:53:52.000Z","msg":"個強姦犯搞你唔通你又同個強姦犯有關係呀"},{"pid":"a2f2796a889eb4a5bbba73700d1510e87d386b71","tid":268210,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T01:07:35.000Z","msg":"由佢啦，一年一度既搵食季節姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"797c60bafb3eee5425a3cc6e8ca5ccd6aab01775","tid":268210,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T01:09:01.000Z","msg":"64果陣又對抗暴政<br />\n垃會果陣又民主回歸<br />\n點撚樣呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1f7b680a2a6d31